<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="like-vt">like <strong><em>vt</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /laɪk/    美 /laɪk/  </p>
<p>[一般不用于进行时]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>喜欢：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>What kind of movie do you like best?
你最喜欢哪种类型的电影？</p></div>

<ul>
<li>like (sb) doing / to do sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He has never liked talking about people behind their backs.
他从来不喜欢在背后议论人。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I'm easy to get along with and I like to make friends.
我容易相处并且喜欢交朋友。</p><footer>2011 辽宁书面表达</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I don't like people spitting in public.
我不喜欢人们在公共场合吐痰。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>like sb / sth + adj:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Do you like your tea strong or weak?
你喜欢茶浓一些还是淡一些？</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>希望；想要：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I'd like a double room.
我想要一个双人间。</p><footer>2015 湖北</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>would / should like to do sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Would you like to join us in the discussion? 
你想和我们一起讨论吗？</p></div>

<ul>
<li>would / should like sb to do sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We'd like you to stay for dinner.
我们希望你能留下来吃饭。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="how-do-you-like">How do you like ...?</h3>
<p>1.<strong>你 (们) 认为…怎么样？</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>How do you like this oil painting?  
你认为这幅油画怎么样？</p><footer>2008 上海</footer></div>

<h3 id="id-like-to">I'd like to.</h3>
<p>1.<strong>[省略句，作答语用] 我愿意。</strong>  </p>
<h3 id="if-you-like">if you like</h3>
<p>1.<strong>如果你愿意：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I can take you there in my car, if you like. 
如果你愿意，我可以开车送你去那里。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Doing housework gives our parents more time to do what they are like and it improves the family relationship.  （2021全国改 改错）  </li>
<li>I want my cafe to have a special theme such as like"Tang Dynasty".  （2019全国 改错）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. 去掉are  2. 去掉like  </p></div>